tooltipText:
Channel a massive blizzard around you, raining a barrage of hail shards upon your enemies while channeling. Periodically pulses $effect:Status_Chilled.hide$ to targets within the area.

Each shard impact deals $hit:Mage_Blizzard_Shard_Hit_AoE$ in a small area around it and applies $effect:Status_Frozen$ to targets with $effect:Status_Chilled.hide$.
name: Mage_Blizzard
